<item>
            <title>[SPR-8817] Support per-script statement separator configuration for SQL scripts</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8817</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have tried to setup an in-memory db with hsql. In one of my scripts there is a stored procedure. Database setup fails when executing this script.&lt;/p&gt;

